To install, unpack the files into the "plugins/truncate-rss" directory

For example

/var/www/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/truncate-rss/
  .
  (files)
  .

Go into the admin tool and click on the settings menu.
You will see a "Truncate-RSS" link in that menu. Click
that and then change any options you wish.

Click save and happy blogging!
